# Binary sensory assets shipped by extensions.
# Models, audio, raw source. These should live in object storage or
# Git LFS, not in the main repo. Extension authors drop them into
# <ext>/assets/ for local development; ship via a separate channel
# (per-extension release tarball, S3 bucket, etc.) when distributing.
